WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.800 line:5%
[On stage]

2
00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:04.200 line:5%
[Applause]

3
00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.000 line:5%
[Music]

4
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:17.000 line:5%
Teresa Teng (singing): The night is dark,
all is still,

5
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:28.500 line:5%
and the moonlight is dim.

6
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:40.500 line:5%
The wind is chilly,
the shadows are swaying;

7
00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:52.500 line:5%
a meteorite traces the sky
and a strange bird cries out.

8
00:00:52.500 --> 00:01:06.000 line:5%
Not even a hint of another person
as I walk alone,

9
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:19.500 line:5%
which scares me out of my wits.

10
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:35.750 line:5%
The gift of money from a beautiful lady
is so affectionate,

11
00:01:35.750 --> 00:01:43.500 line:5%
it makes me feel both ashamed of myself
and fond of her.

12
00:01:43.500 --> 00:02:04.000 line:5%
I see that the garden gate is ajar.

13
00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:24.000 line:5%
Xuechun must be inside.
